<item>
            <title>[DOXIA-772] AbstractSink.sectionTitle() calls Sink.sectionTitle(...) method with invalid level argument</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DOXIA-772</link>
                <project id="12317230" key="DOXIA">Maven Doxia (Moved to GitHub Issues)</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;According to &lt;a href=&quot;https://maven.apache.org/doxia/doxia/doxia-sink-api/apidocs/org/apache/maven/doxia/sink/Sink.html#sectionTitle-int-org.apache.maven.doxia.sink.SinkEventAttributes-&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maven.apache.org/doxia/doxia/doxia-sink-api/apidocs/org/apache/maven/doxia/sink/Sink.html#sectionTitle-int-org.apache.maven.doxia.sink.SinkEventAttributes-&lt;/a&gt; the &lt;tt&gt;level&lt;/tt&gt; argument must be between 1 and 6. However &lt;tt&gt;AbstractSink.sectionTitle()&lt;/tt&gt; calls it with &lt;tt&gt;level&lt;/tt&gt; being 0 (&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/maven-doxia/blob/ef20da287e49dbbe4ac92a82e7593b3c897ce126/doxia-core/src/main/java/org/apache/maven/doxia/sink/impl/AbstractSink.java#L84&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/maven-doxia/blob/ef20da287e49dbbe4ac92a82e7593b3c897ce126/doxia-core/src/main/java/org/apache/maven/doxia/sink/impl/AbstractSink.java#L84&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="13603596">DOXIA-772</key>
            <summary>AbstractSink.sectionTitle() calls Sink.sectionTitle(...) method with invalid level argument</summary>
                <type id="1" iconUrl="https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/viewavatar?size=xsmall&amp;avatarId=21133&amp;avatarType=issuetype">Bug</type>
