                                    <reporter username="kwin">Konrad Windszus</reporter>
                        <labels>
                    </labels>
                <created>Thu, 2 Jan 2025 17:00:00 +0000</created>
                <updated>Tue, 15 Jul 2025 10:00:01 +0000</updated>
                            <resolved>Thu, 2 Jan 2025 18:30:04 +0000</resolved>
                                                    <fixVersion>2.1.0</fixVersion>
                                        <due></due>
                            <votes>0</votes>
                                    <watches>3</watches>
                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="17909348" author="kwin" created="Thu, 2 Jan 2025 17:04:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=michael-o&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;michael-o&quot;&gt;michael-o&lt;/a&gt; Seems that at least the XHTML sink always ignored level &amp;lt; 1 (i.e. that method always was a noop there. Not sure about the other sinks though. WDYT?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17909354" author="kwin" created="Thu, 2 Jan 2025 17:21:35 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Also &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/maven-doxia/blob/0760ba1be055dd9865a09269f2d23967967d5aa2/doxia-modules/doxia-module-xdoc/src/main/java/org/apache/maven/doxia/module/xdoc/XdocSink.java#L334&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;XDoc&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/maven-doxia/blob/0760ba1be055dd9865a09269f2d23967967d5aa2/doxia-modules/doxia-module-apt/src/main/java/org/apache/maven/doxia/module/apt/AptSink.java#L328&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;APT&lt;/a&gt; never implemented &lt;tt&gt;Sink.sectionTitle()&lt;/tt&gt;. so it  probably would be good to explicitly make it a Noop in &lt;tt&gt;AbstractSink&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17909357" author="michael-o" created="Thu, 2 Jan 2025 17:35:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Agree, let&apos;s make it consistent. 0 makes no sense to me.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17909393" author="kwin" created="Thu, 2 Jan 2025 18:30:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Deprecated sectionTitle() and sectionTitle_() in &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/maven-doxia/commit/431fb56aa069e1b56cfd98364578f18ceb834660&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/maven-doxia/commit/431fb56aa069e1b56cfd98364578f18ceb834660&lt;/a&gt; and made them no-ops.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="18006247" author="sparsick" created="Tue, 15 Jul 2025 10:00:01 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This project has moved from Jira to GitHub Issues. This issue was migrated to &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/maven-doxia/issues/886&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;apache/maven-doxia#886&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
